      <title>耶伦建议在日元飙升后对货币干预保持谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/yellen-counsels-caution-on-currency-intervention-after-yen-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦承认本周日元汇率大幅波动，尽管她拒绝透露日本是否进行了干预以支持日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/yellen-counsels-caution-on-currency-intervention-after-yen-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 23:51:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芒格去世后，巴菲特后的伯克希尔成为奥马哈焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/a-post-buffett-berkshire-is-omaha-focus-after-munger-s-passing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 周六的年会让股东们了解到，如果没有查理·芒格 (Charlie Munger)（去年去世，享年 99 岁），该集团将如何运营。接下来的问题是：如果没有沃伦·巴菲特 (Warren巴菲特)，该公司将如何运营？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/a-post-buffett-berkshire-is-omaha-focus-after-munger-s-passing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 21:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国马克龙呼吁重启与中国的经济关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/france-s-macron-calls-for-reset-of-economic-ties-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙呼吁更新法国与中国的经济关系，而该国领导人习近平预计将前往法国进行国事访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/france-s-macron-calls-for-reset-of-economic-ties-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非拉马福萨相信政府能够稳定债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-confident-government-can-stabilize-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，他相信政府已经在服务支出与控制国家不断膨胀的债务水平之间找到了平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-confident-government-can-stabilize-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 20:54:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
