      <title>贝利的降息计划将与鲍威尔的有所不同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/boe-rate-cuts-uk-interest-rate-plan-will-differ-from-the-fed-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行可能会在未来一周就是否计划在今年夏天降息发出更明确的信号，就像投资者押注宽松政策的延迟前景一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/boe-rate-cuts-uk-interest-rate-plan-will-differ-from-the-fed-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ISS 建议波音投资者投票反对首席执行官薪酬方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/iss-recommends-boeing-investors-vote-against-ceo-pay-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[机构股东服务公司敦促波音公司投资者投票反对其首席执行官 3280 万美元的薪酬方案，理由是对特别股权奖励和长期激励补助“大幅增加”的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/iss-recommends-boeing-investors-vote-against-ceo-pay-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 17:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着投资的增加，加密初创公司的估值大幅提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/crypto-startups-turbocharge-valuations-as-investment-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币初创公司正在通过积极的融资形式将估值推向快车道，这反映了数字资产行业的复苏以及风险基金投入资金的愿望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/crypto-startups-turbocharge-valuations-as-investment-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔现金储备再创新高，盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/buffett-s-berkshire-says-cash-hits-record-as-earnings-gain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者沃伦·巴菲特面临大宗交易稀缺的局面，伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司的现金储备再创纪录。受其保险业务的推动，该公司的营业利润也有所增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/buffett-s-berkshire-says-cash-hits-record-as-earnings-gain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 12:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃弗顿足球俱乐部买家被指控欺诈并在诉讼中双重抵押资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/lenders-to-777-partners-allege-fraud-double-pledging-in-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[777 Partners 的贷款人指控其存在欺诈行为，声称这家总部位于迈阿密的投资公司以 3.5 亿美元的资产为抵押借款，而这些资产并不属于 777 Partners、该公司并不存在或已经承诺给其他人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-04/lenders-to-777-partners-allege-fraud-double-pledging-in-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
